            <h3 style="color: #007bff; font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 10px; transition: color 0.3s ease; font-weight: bold;">Significance:</h3>
            <ul style="line-height: 1.6; font-size: 1.1rem; padding-left: 20px;">
